as the Commandery Princess Consort An)

3
00:00:16,359 --> 00:00:17,490
(attending a palace banquet.)

4
00:00:18,359 --> 00:00:19,559
(I was somewhat nervous.)

5
00:00:20,239 --> 00:00:21,790
(Fortunately, everything went smoothly.)

6
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:23,920
(But I never expected)

7
00:00:23,930 --> 00:00:26,380
(that a jumping human skull
would appear during the banquet.)

8
00:00:28,399 --> 00:00:29,719
(Such a bizarre case occurred.)

9
00:00:30,199 --> 00:00:32,079
(The deceased must be given justice.)

10
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:34,700
(Chu Chu did everything she could
to protect the skull)

11
00:00:34,719 --> 00:00:35,870
(and preserve the evidence.)

12
00:00:36,300 --> 00:00:38,799
(I also argued firmly on behalf
of the Three Judicial Offices,)

13
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,520
(and ultimately obtained
the authority to investigate the case.)

